## Scope

This report is a deterministic, CSV-grounded comparison of two finished
ClawModeler runs in the same workspace. It reports **added**, **removed**,
and **changed** rows for every tracked artifact — engine outputs
(`project_scores.csv`, `vmt_screening.csv`) and the Planner Pack series
(`ceqa_vmt.csv`, `lapm_exhibit.csv`, `rtp_chapter_*.csv`,
`equity_lens.csv`, `atp_packet.csv`) — so the lead agency can explain
*what moved* between RTP draft iterations, scenario edits, or project
list revisions.

Artifacts that are not present in one or both runs are reported
explicitly; no values are silently defaulted. Every added / removed /
changed row is mirrored as a `run_diff_row` fact_block, and every
artifact summary as a `run_diff_summary` fact_block, so downstream
narrative and chat turns remain under the ClawModeler citation
contract.

